item.title: SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee_Epo_Version36
item.description: SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee_Epo_Version36 Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee_Epo_Version36 data type represents a single McAfee Secure anti-virus/spyware software component that uses the ePolicy Orchestrator version 3.6 backend. Local epoVersion The version of ePolicy Orchestrator that the anti-virus/spyware client communicates with. Type: string hardwareId Hardware Identification Number for the server this Software Component is installed upon. Type: integer id An ID number identifying this Software Component (Software Installation) Type: integer
